This Facebook post is a fundraising campaign for EduActiv, a non-profit organization focused on helping children in vulnerable situations.  The post promotes a Christmas fundraising campaign to provide gifts and necessities to children in need. There is no mention of any political candidate or party, nor any attempt to influence voters in any election. The content is focused solely on raising funds for a charitable cause.  The fact that it's categorized as "POLITICAL" in the Facebook Ad Library is likely due to the broad definition of political advertising, which can sometimes encompass social issue campaigns. However, the content itself does not meet the criteria for electoral propaganda as defined by Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015.  The campaign's timeframe (November 12th - December 17th) does not coincide with any specific election period mentioned in the provided context.  The post's objective is clearly charitable, not electoral.
</electoral-propaganda-analysis>
